        <div class="max-w-full mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <p class="text-[10px] md:text-[11px] font-medium text-slate-400 text-center">
                Explorando la Autopoiesis a través de modelos computacionales.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[9px] md:text-[10px] text-slate-600 font-mono text-center text-slate-500">
                Referencia: Varela, F.G., Maturana, H.R., & Uribe, R. (1974). Autopoiesis: The organization of living systems, its characterization and a model. <em>BioSystems, 5</em>, 187-196.
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</BaseLayout>
